CREDIT UNION
"Introductory interest rate reverts to our then current credit card interest rate after six months which can be found at
peopleschoicecu.com.au - the applicable variable interest rate will be determined by the information you provide and
the assessment of your application and will be confirmed in your credit contract. Highest revert rate is currently
15.75%p.a. after six months. A purchase is only interest free if the statement balances (recording the purchase) for the
current and preceding months are paid in full when due, otherwise interest will apply from the date of the purchase.
-Cash advances and balance transfers do not qualify for the interest free period and attract interest from the date of
the transaction Fees and charges apply. People's Choice Credit Union, a trading name of Australian Central Credit
Union Ltd, ABN 11 087 651125, Australian Credit Licence (244310).
